text: Schuchertinia is a genus of commensal athecate hydroids in the family Hydractiniidae. ==Species== The World Register of Marine Species includes the following species in the genus: *Schuchertinia allmanii (Bonnevie, 1898) *Schuchertinia antonii (Miglietta, 2006) *Schuchertinia conchicola (Yamada, 1947) *Schuchertinia epiconcha (Stechow, 1908) *Schuchertinia milleri (Torrey, 1902) *Schuchertinia reticulata (Hirohito, 1988) *Schuchertinia uchidai (Yamada, 1947) ==References== Category:Anthomedusae
title: Schuchertinia
